snippet.title: Tray Racers! - Official Developer Commentary and Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The world ended…But the fun didn’t! Race solo, or with your pals across the adorable post-apocalyptic world of Tray Racers! Grab a tray, surf the dunes, and get ready to SLIDE, DRIFT and TRICK your way to the finish line in this cute and colorful party racer, built for online multiplayer!

Developer Bit Loom dives deep into Tray Racer! and showcases what makes the game special and updates fans on playtests happening in the future.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
